OL,3,CCritics say plans to fix cladding is
OL,4,C'totally laughable and unachievable'
OL,6,FDeputy Prime Minister Angela Rayner
OL,7,Fdescribed the plans as "decisive
OL,8,Faction" and said the "pace of
OL,9,Fremediation has been far too slow for
OL,10,Ffar too long."
OL,12,FHowever, campaigners have labelled
OL,13,Fthem as "extremely disappointing"
OL,14,Fproposals that will "only make a
OL,15,Fhorribly complicated process worse".
OL,17,FRuth Guest has owned her apartment in
OL,18,FManchester for 20 years and is
OL,19,Fdoubtful the target will be reached.
