OL,3,CCritics say plans to fix cladding is
OL,4,C'totally laughable and unachievable'
OL,6,FShe said "Like many of the
OL,7,Fleaseholders in the country I was
OL,8,Fstuck in a property that we couldn't
OL,9,Fsell.
OL,11,F"It was a zero valued property. We
OL,12,Fcouldn't get a mortgage for it so life
OL,13,Fbecame in limbo. We couldn't do
OL,14,Fanything.
OL,16,F"We have had leaseholders who have had
OL,17,Fto put off their wedding plans or
OL,18,Fstarting a family. Their career
OL,19,Fprospects have been put on hold.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
