OL,3,CCritics say plans to fix cladding is
OL,4,C'totally laughable and unachievable'
OL,6,F"If they have been able to move they
OL,7,Fhave become accidental landlords
OL,8,Fbecause they cannot sell their
OL,9,Fproperty. It is just crazy. It is
OL,10,Fheartbreaking."
OL,12,FRuth is waiting for a 'waking watch'
OL,13,Fbill - a fire safety system where
OL,14,Fsuitably trained staff continually
OL,15,Fpatrol the floors and the external
OL,16,Fperimeter of a building to maintain
OL,17,Fthe safety of occupants.
