OL,6,FRuth said "It is crazy. Fortunately
OL,7,Ffor me I am a qualifying lease holder
OL,8,Fbecause I own less that four
OL,9,Fproperties so I have got protection up
OL,10,Fto #1000 per year.
OL,12,F"For non qualifying leaseholders who
OL,13,Fown four or more properties they are
OL,14,Fliable for the whole cost. We are
OL,15,Fsitting here as innocent victims.
