OL,3,CCritics say plans to fix cladding is
OL,4,C'totally laughable and unachievable'
OL,6,F"I just cannot see how a 2029 deadline
OL,7,Fis achievable. Four and a half years
OL,8,Fafter the building safety fund opened
OL,9,Fwe are not really anymore forward. How
OL,10,Fare they going to achieve it in five
OL,11,Fyears?
OL,13,F"It is totally laughable and
OL,14,Funachievable.
OL,16,F"This is my safe haven or should be my
OL,17,Fsafe haven but every time I open my
OL,18,Fdoor I get a reminder. That 'waking
OL,19,Fwatch' walking around. A constant
OL,20,Freminder of how dangerous this
OL,21,Fbuilding is."
